text: Viktor Baranov (born 1893, date of death unknown) was a Russian diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1893 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Russia Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn
